WEBVTT

00:00:01.420 --> 00:00:05.750 align:middle
B Komachi

00:00:02.670 --> 00:00:05.040 align:middle
This story is a work of fiction.

00:00:06.460 --> 00:00:10.330 align:middle
Actually, most everything in this world is fiction.

00:00:11.920 --> 00:00:13.000 align:middle
They fabricate...

00:00:13.670 --> 00:00:14.630 align:middle
exaggerate...

00:00:15.750 --> 00:00:18.250 align:middle
and thoroughly conceal anything inconvenient.

00:00:19.630 --> 00:00:24.790 align:middle
That being the case, the idol fan is one
who wants to be skillfully lied to.

00:00:26.330 --> 00:00:29.460 align:middle
In this world, lies are weapons.

00:00:30.830 --> 00:00:32.750 align:middle
Ai!

00:00:33.330 --> 00:00:36.750 align:middle
I wish I could've witnessed her cuteness in person!

00:00:39.830 --> 00:00:42.960 align:middle
The idol group B Komachi's absolute ace...

00:00:42.960 --> 00:00:44.330 align:middle
Their unshakable center...

00:00:44.880 --> 00:00:47.210 align:middle
The supremely pretty 16-year-old girl...

00:00:47.500 --> 00:00:48.250 align:middle
Ai!

00:00:49.710 --> 00:00:51.460 align:middle
It's been four years since their formation!

00:00:51.460 --> 00:00:54.750 align:middle
They gradually gained popularity,
their media exposure increased,

00:00:54.750 --> 00:00:57.290 align:middle
and it feels like the public has
now finally discovered them!

00:00:57.710 --> 00:01:01.580 align:middle
This is where she really takes off!
Her stardom is now close at-

00:01:02.080 --> 00:01:05.880 align:middle
Why are you playing a DVD in a patient's room?

00:01:06.330 --> 00:01:08.420 align:middle
It goes without saying it's rather odd.

00:01:10.420 --> 00:01:13.000 align:middle
Observing something beautiful is good for one's health.

00:01:14.040 --> 00:01:16.710 align:middle
I mean, it's not like there are any idol concerts
this far out in the countryside.

00:01:16.920 --> 00:01:18.630 align:middle
This is a form of medical practice.

00:01:19.130 --> 00:01:21.130 align:middle
It's proselytizing, plain and simple.

00:01:21.130 --> 00:01:24.040 align:middle
Please don't make it our hospital's official position.

00:01:24.790 --> 00:01:26.880 align:middle
Oh, that reminds me, sensei.

00:01:27.040 --> 00:01:29.080 align:middle
Just now, it was trending on Twitter that...

00:01:29.420 --> 00:01:31.170 align:middle
WHAT?!

00:01:31.380 --> 00:01:34.580 align:middle
Ai of B Komachi

00:01:31.380 --> 00:01:34.580 align:middle
Goes on Hiatus Due to Poor Health

00:01:31.580 --> 00:01:34.580 align:middle
Ai is going on hiatus?!

00:01:35.790 --> 00:01:37.670 align:middle
You really are a true believer.

00:01:38.460 --> 00:01:41.670 align:middle
She's 16, isn't she? I guess you're a lolicon.

00:01:41.670 --> 00:01:43.000 align:middle
I only ask you don't call me that.

00:01:44.210 --> 00:01:46.790 align:middle
I've got my reasons, okay?

00:01:48.250 --> 00:01:50.960 align:middle
I did my residency at this same hospital, you see.

00:01:51.750 --> 00:01:55.580 align:middle
In those days, I often slacked off
in patients' rooms same as now.

00:01:55.580 --> 00:01:56.500 align:middle
Shape up.

00:01:56.960 --> 00:02:02.170 align:middle
Sarina Tendouji

00:01:57.580 --> 00:02:01.750 align:middle
One of the patients I met back then changed my destiny.

00:02:02.750 --> 00:02:04.670 align:middle
And this girl is Mei-Mei!

00:02:04.670 --> 00:02:06.080 align:middle
Her dancing is great!

00:02:06.670 --> 00:02:07.630 align:middle
Hmm...

00:02:08.040 --> 00:02:11.040 align:middle
Ari-pyan and Kyun-pan are good singers,

00:02:11.710 --> 00:02:14.080 align:middle
but my fave is...

00:02:14.380 --> 00:02:16.210 align:middle
without a doubt Ai!

00:02:17.040 --> 00:02:21.880 align:middle
She's about my age, but she's so grown-up
looking and great at singing and dancing!

00:02:22.420 --> 00:02:24.170 align:middle
And what a pretty face she has...

00:02:24.170 --> 00:02:26.790 align:middle
If I could be reborn, that's the face I want.

00:02:27.920 --> 00:02:31.580 align:middle
What's this "reborn" nonsense? Don't be silly.

00:02:32.920 --> 00:02:34.710 align:middle
Not much of a dreamer, are you?

00:02:36.790 --> 00:02:42.170 align:middle
Haven't you thought about what it'd be like
if you were born as a celebrity's child?

00:02:43.080 --> 00:02:47.750 align:middle
Like, if you had looks and connections right from birth.

00:02:48.460 --> 00:02:49.170 align:middle
Nope.

00:02:49.500 --> 00:02:51.460 align:middle
So you really don't have any dreams...

00:02:52.290 --> 00:02:54.000 align:middle
You're cute yourself, Sarina-chan.

00:02:54.500 --> 00:02:56.420 align:middle
There's no need for you to be reborn.

00:02:59.040 --> 00:03:01.880 align:middle
After you're discharged,
become an idol yourself if you want.

00:03:02.290 --> 00:03:03.960 align:middle
I'll be your fan if you do.

00:03:03.960 --> 00:03:04.960 align:middle
Really?

00:03:05.210 --> 00:03:07.250 align:middle
I love you, sensei! Marry me!

00:03:07.250 --> 00:03:09.960 align:middle
Forgive me, but I'd be as good as dead socially.

00:03:10.920 --> 00:03:12.500 align:middle
Okay, Mr. Moralist...

00:03:12.750 --> 00:03:17.080 align:middle
A shame, isn't it? But I'll seriously
consider it once you turn 16.

00:03:18.960 --> 00:03:20.420 align:middle
Sixteen, huh?

00:03:21.630 --> 00:03:23.880 align:middle
You're a big meanie.

00:03:24.250 --> 00:03:25.920 align:middle
It's a practical plan, right?

00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:37.420 align:middle
An anaplastic astrocytoma...
She was just 12 years old.

00:03:39.170 --> 00:03:42.630 align:middle
If she were still alive today, she'd be 16 just like Ai.

00:03:43.500 --> 00:03:47.460 align:middle
I suppose I followed Sarina-chan's favorite idol,
superimposing the two of them in my mind.

00:03:48.710 --> 00:03:50.750 align:middle
Her walking the path toward her dreams...

00:03:51.290 --> 00:03:53.500 align:middle
I just want to see that is all.

00:03:54.040 --> 00:03:55.130 align:middle
Makes sense.

00:03:55.790 --> 00:03:57.630 align:middle
So you're quite the lolicon, after all.

00:03:57.630 --> 00:03:58.920 align:middle
Were you even listening?!

00:03:58.920 --> 00:04:01.460 align:middle
That was quite the touching story I recalled!

00:04:02.210 --> 00:04:05.540 align:middle
There's something graphic about
the way you're obsessed with her.

00:04:06.080 --> 00:04:10.040 align:middle
Aren't you just using Sarina-chan as
an excuse to release your own desires?

00:04:10.040 --> 00:04:14.460 align:middle
Ridiculous! I swear in Sarina-chan's name that
I'm supporting her with the purest of hearts!

00:04:14.960 --> 00:04:19.330 align:middle
But, if that Ai girl appeared and
asked you to date her, wouldn't you?

00:04:23.380 --> 00:04:26.920 align:middle
Well, lunch break is over. Let's get back to work.

00:04:26.920 --> 00:04:31.380 align:middle
How about it, Sensei? Swearing in the name
of Sarina-chan, what's your answer?

00:04:31.880 --> 00:04:33.830 align:middle
Internal Medicine 2

00:04:31.880 --> 00:04:33.830 align:middle
Internal Medicine 1

00:04:31.880 --> 00:04:33.830 align:middle
Ultrasound Room

00:04:31.880 --> 00:04:33.830 align:middle
Ophthalmology

00:04:31.880 --> 00:04:33.830 align:middle
CT Room

00:04:32.880 --> 00:04:37.920 align:middle
Still, I am worried about Ai... I hope she gets
healthy and makes a comeback.

00:04:38.790 --> 00:04:43.750 align:middle
Obstetrics and

00:04:38.790 --> 00:04:43.750 align:middle
Gynecology

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:42.630 align:middle
Hello, thank you for waiting.

00:04:44.500 --> 00:04:48.040 align:middle
Let's see... So this is your first visit, Hoshino-san?

00:04:48.290 --> 00:04:48.960 align:middle
Yes.

00:04:49.710 --> 00:04:52.540 align:middle
Judging by her belly, she's about 20 weeks along now.

00:04:52.960 --> 00:04:55.630 align:middle
That's rather late for an initial examination.

00:04:56.630 --> 00:05:00.080 align:middle
She is 16 years of age... I see,
she must be dealing with some things.

00:05:00.580 --> 00:05:04.130 align:middle
Must be one of those girls who gets this
far along without being able to consult anyone.

00:05:04.580 --> 00:05:05.920 align:middle
Are you her father?

00:05:06.130 --> 00:05:08.250 align:middle
Well, on paper...

00:05:09.000 --> 00:05:15.630 align:middle
She grew up in a children's home, and
I'm her de facto guardian, or rather her guarantor.

00:05:15.630 --> 00:05:16.750 align:middle
Oh, I see.

00:05:17.710 --> 00:05:22.210 align:middle
Sixteen, raised in a children's home.
I feel like I've heard this story before.

00:05:22.790 --> 00:05:23.750 align:middle
It's just like...

00:05:34.130 --> 00:05:39.040 align:middle
Sensei, how is it looking? Any chance
she just has a terrible case of constipation...?

00:05:39.250 --> 00:05:41.380 align:middle
In that case, she'd be dead already.

00:05:41.710 --> 00:05:42.960 align:middle
I'm doin' fine on that front!

00:05:43.250 --> 00:05:44.830 align:middle
No problems today either!

00:05:47.540 --> 00:05:52.210 align:middle
First off, you'll need an examination.
I need to get everything ready, so please wait here.

00:05:52.380 --> 00:05:55.000 align:middle
Obstetrics and

00:05:52.380 --> 00:05:55.000 align:middle
Gynecology

00:05:55.290 --> 00:05:56.880 align:middle
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!

00:05:56.880 --> 00:05:58.630 align:middle
Man, is that really her?!

00:05:58.960 --> 00:06:00.420 align:middle
Could she just be a dead ringer for Ai?!

00:06:00.420 --> 00:06:03.920 align:middle
Nah, no way a years-long fan
like myself would be mistaken!

00:06:04.290 --> 00:06:08.710 align:middle
Wow, Ai is super cute in person!

00:06:08.880 --> 00:06:10.250 align:middle
NO!

00:06:10.500 --> 00:06:13.630 align:middle
My favorite idol is pregnant!

00:06:14.080 --> 00:06:17.750 align:middle
It's such a shock I feel like I'm gonna vomit.

00:06:18.130 --> 00:06:19.040 align:middle
Ai...

00:06:19.630 --> 00:06:21.580 align:middle
how in the world did this happen?

00:06:21.580 --> 00:06:23.080 align:middle
Yeah, seriously!

00:06:23.630 --> 00:06:26.420 align:middle
As your agency's president, why didn't you consult me?

00:06:26.670 --> 00:06:28.540 align:middle
Who's the father anyway?

00:06:29.330 --> 00:06:30.130 align:middle
Well...

00:06:35.000 --> 00:06:36.170 align:middle
that's a secret!

00:06:36.170 --> 00:06:39.920 align:middle
"A secret"?! Well, no point belaboring it, then.

00:06:49.290 --> 00:06:53.080 align:middle
The results of the examination are as follows:
20 weeks pregnant, twins.

00:06:53.880 --> 00:06:54.750 align:middle
"Twins"?

00:06:56.670 --> 00:06:57.580 align:middle
Twins...

00:06:58.210 --> 00:07:00.500 align:middle
Ai, you serious about carrying them to term?

00:07:00.960 --> 00:07:04.380 align:middle
If it gets out that you've become
pregnant at 16 and given birth...

00:07:05.210 --> 00:07:09.500 align:middle
your career and my agency will be finished.

00:07:11.790 --> 00:07:13.290 align:middle
What are your thoughts, Sensei?

00:07:18.210 --> 00:07:20.790 align:middle
The final decision rests with you.

00:07:21.710 --> 00:07:23.380 align:middle
Really think it through before deciding.

00:07:24.920 --> 00:07:27.670 align:middle
As a doctor, that is all I'm able to say.

00:07:30.460 --> 00:07:32.000 align:middle
As a doctor... anyway.

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:33.380 align:middle
And now, onto our next story.

00:07:33.380 --> 00:07:34.750 align:middle
Ugh, for real?

00:07:35.250 --> 00:07:37.960 align:middle
Surprise

00:07:35.250 --> 00:07:37.960 align:middle
Announcement

00:07:35.250 --> 00:07:37.960 align:middle
Entertainer Ponta and Idol MIU

00:07:35.250 --> 00:07:37.960 align:middle
are married and expecting

00:07:35.380 --> 00:07:42.920 align:middle
Today, popular entertainer Ponta-san and idol MIU-san
held a joint press conference announcing their marriage.

00:07:35.580 --> 00:07:37.710 align:middle
Man, I really liked MIU...

00:07:38.170 --> 00:07:40.170 align:middle
Well, that's rather timely...

00:07:40.170 --> 00:07:46.000 align:middle
Wait, if I die now, there's a chance
I'll be reborn as an idol's kid... right?

00:07:42.920 --> 00:07:46.000 align:middle
MIU-san is currently five-months pregnant.

00:07:46.330 --> 00:07:48.170 align:middle
That's pretty messed up, dude.

00:07:48.710 --> 00:07:53.000 align:middle
Still, can you really stan an idol
who's got a husband and kids?

00:07:56.710 --> 00:08:00.920 align:middle
Even if you've got a guy you've fallen for,
I'll still keep supporting you.

00:08:02.040 --> 00:08:08.710 align:middle
That said, if you give birth to these children, I suspect
I won't be able to see you soar to greater heights.

00:08:10.000 --> 00:08:12.500 align:middle
I guess the views of fans are pretty self-centered...

00:08:13.080 --> 00:08:15.130 align:middle
You think so too, don't you, Sarina-chan?

00:08:16.380 --> 00:08:18.080 align:middle
Oh, Sensei.

00:08:18.080 --> 00:08:19.420 align:middle
Hoshino-san.

00:08:20.540 --> 00:08:22.750 align:middle
It's not good for you to be out on a windy night.

00:08:22.750 --> 00:08:24.750 align:middle
I'm bundled up, so I'll be fine.

00:08:27.170 --> 00:08:31.540 align:middle
I chose this place based on the president's
recommendation, but it sure is lovely!

00:08:32.460 --> 00:08:35.790 align:middle
There are so many stars even at dusk.

00:08:37.170 --> 00:08:40.130 align:middle
You could never see this back in Tokyo.

00:08:42.710 --> 00:08:46.920 align:middle
Did you come all the way out here to the countryside
because you'd be recognized in Tokyo?

00:08:47.500 --> 00:08:48.250 align:middle
Oh?

00:08:48.670 --> 00:08:50.580 align:middle
Did I mention my work?

00:08:51.420 --> 00:08:55.670 align:middle
Long ago, one of my patients was a big fan of yours.

00:08:56.080 --> 00:09:02.290 align:middle
Aww... I thought even the doctors here would
be old men and nobody would find me out.

00:09:02.540 --> 00:09:04.880 align:middle
Guess there's no hiding my overflowing aura.

00:09:04.880 --> 00:09:06.080 align:middle
Awkward, awkward!

00:09:06.080 --> 00:09:07.500 align:middle
Her self-confidence is cute.

00:09:08.630 --> 00:09:11.420 align:middle
So, are you gonna give up being an idol?

00:09:11.420 --> 00:09:12.460 align:middle
Why?

00:09:12.460 --> 00:09:13.290 align:middle
No way.

00:09:13.750 --> 00:09:15.250 align:middle
But, that means...

00:09:16.330 --> 00:09:19.040 align:middle
I don't have a family, you see.

00:09:19.540 --> 00:09:21.710 align:middle
I always longed for one.

00:09:23.000 --> 00:09:25.750 align:middle
I'm carrying twins, right?

00:09:27.080 --> 00:09:30.500 align:middle
I'm sure our family will be a cheerful and fun one!

00:09:31.750 --> 00:09:33.290 align:middle
You're gonna give birth...

00:09:33.580 --> 00:09:35.330 align:middle
and also continue being an idol.

00:09:35.630 --> 00:09:37.540 align:middle
So, that must mean...

00:09:37.920 --> 00:09:40.420 align:middle
Yep, I won't make it public.

00:09:41.210 --> 00:09:43.210 align:middle
Idols are objects of worship, you know?

00:09:43.210 --> 00:09:45.880 align:middle
They sparkle through the magic of lies.

00:09:46.830 --> 00:09:49.420 align:middle
Lies are the most exquisite love!

00:09:49.830 --> 00:09:54.170 align:middle
Being able to conceal a kid or two just works
to show someone's a top-class idol.

00:09:54.830 --> 00:10:02.880 align:middle
Piling on lie after lie, we look happy as we sing on stage
no matter what struggles we might face. What a fun job!

00:10:04.250 --> 00:10:08.710 align:middle
Still... The happiness part's something
that I wanna experience for real.

00:10:09.250 --> 00:10:13.170 align:middle
No one realizes it, but we've got
our own feelings and lives, too.

00:10:14.250 --> 00:10:18.710 align:middle
Happiness as a mother, and happiness as an idol...

00:10:19.250 --> 00:10:21.250 align:middle
It might be normal to have only one...

00:10:22.000 --> 00:10:23.330 align:middle
but I want both!

00:10:23.830 --> 00:10:26.290 align:middle
Ai Hoshino's a greedy girl, you know!

00:10:27.130 --> 00:10:32.710 align:middle
The idol I knew as Ai is far more bold, cunning,
and strong than I ever imagined.

00:10:33.880 --> 00:10:36.000 align:middle
She shone as bright as the first start of evening.

00:10:37.540 --> 00:10:38.750 align:middle
I've reached a settlement.

00:10:38.750 --> 00:10:39.540 align:middle
Huh?

00:10:39.960 --> 00:10:43.500 align:middle
My views as a doctor and as a fan have now aligned.

00:10:44.920 --> 00:10:51.130 align:middle
Ai Hoshino, I will perform the delivery,
ensuring you safely give birth to healthy children.

00:10:52.960 --> 00:10:55.920 align:middle
If that's what will make you happy, I'll go along with it.

00:10:56.630 --> 00:11:05.380 align:middle
After all, you're hopelessly an idol,
and I am hopelessly your fan.

00:11:08.540 --> 00:11:11.040 align:middle
Alright, let's get down to business.

00:11:11.580 --> 00:11:14.710 align:middle
As a start, you should use
an assumed name here at the hospital.

00:11:14.710 --> 00:11:15.460 align:middle
Okay.

00:11:17.250 --> 00:11:20.670 align:middle
In a case like yours, a cesarean section
will likely be necessary.

00:11:21.790 --> 00:11:28.500 align:middle
If one of the baby's skulls is large, for someone with your
build it's common for the pelvis to not open enough.

00:11:28.960 --> 00:11:30.080 align:middle
Oh, really?

00:11:30.670 --> 00:11:33.380 align:middle
A scar on her belly will spell trouble for her job...

00:11:33.380 --> 00:11:35.630 align:middle
Sensei, aren't there other options?

00:11:35.960 --> 00:11:40.210 align:middle
Painless delivery, Sophrology... Well...

00:11:40.210 --> 00:11:43.330 align:middle
Whatever's fine. I feel super healthy.

00:11:43.710 --> 00:11:44.750 align:middle
Ai...

00:11:44.750 --> 00:11:47.580 align:middle
It'll be fine. I can handle a natural delivery.

00:11:48.040 --> 00:11:50.000 align:middle
I mean, they're my kids, right?

00:11:50.000 --> 00:11:52.380 align:middle
They're sure to be attractive and have small faces.

00:11:52.380 --> 00:11:54.790 align:middle
There you go again...

00:11:56.920 --> 00:12:01.040 align:middle
Perhaps I became a doctor for this very moment.

00:12:02.540 --> 00:12:05.460 align:middle
I'll see that they're delivered
as safely and surely as possible.

00:12:07.250 --> 00:12:09.420 align:middle
I vow to protect your family.

00:12:10.630 --> 00:12:13.830 align:middle
If I'm being honest, I do have mixed feelings.

00:12:15.080 --> 00:12:17.170 align:middle
But I've done everything I can to hide that.

00:12:18.920 --> 00:12:20.170 align:middle
Lies are love.

00:12:20.830 --> 00:12:24.750 align:middle
I've come to see that phrase in
a good light - stars truly are amazing.

00:12:25.290 --> 00:12:27.670 align:middle
40 Weeks

00:12:27.670 --> 00:12:30.080 align:middle
Expected Delivery Date

00:12:30.500 --> 00:12:32.130 align:middle
Thanks for today, Sensei.

00:12:32.540 --> 00:12:34.210 align:middle
But come back as soon as I call, okay?

00:12:34.420 --> 00:12:36.750 align:middle
Sure thing. Besides, I live really close by.

00:12:37.170 --> 00:12:40.080 align:middle
Well, if I don't make it,
another doctor will attend to you anyway.

00:12:40.080 --> 00:12:41.710 align:middle
No, I want you.

00:12:41.920 --> 00:12:44.290 align:middle
I'm just joking. See you later.

00:12:44.630 --> 00:12:45.170 align:middle
Okay.

00:12:47.880 --> 00:12:53.830 align:middle
Once this is over, I'll lose my connection to Ai...
and we'll go back to just being an idol and her fan.

00:12:54.830 --> 00:13:01.290 align:middle
I got a glimpse of her hidden side, but I feel that
I actually came to like her straightforward personality.

00:13:02.540 --> 00:13:05.750 align:middle
I feel I can root for her happiness from the bottom of my-

00:13:05.750 --> 00:13:06.630 align:middle
Hey, buddy.

00:13:06.630 --> 00:13:08.420 align:middle
Are you Ai Hoshino's doctor?

00:13:11.420 --> 00:13:13.250 align:middle
She's using an assumed name.

00:13:13.750 --> 00:13:18.710 align:middle
Even if you spotted her at the hospital, why do you know
her family name, which has never been made public.

00:13:19.630 --> 00:13:20.710 align:middle
Are you affiliated with her?

00:13:21.040 --> 00:13:22.330 align:middle
Can I get your name?

00:13:24.080 --> 00:13:24.920 align:middle
Hey!

00:13:29.250 --> 00:13:30.790 align:middle
Could this guy be a stalker?

00:13:30.790 --> 00:13:33.460 align:middle
And his timing, with Ai just about to give birth...

00:13:36.250 --> 00:13:39.790 align:middle
Dammit! Making me rush down
a mountain trail like this...

00:13:40.630 --> 00:13:41.670 align:middle
Where'd he go?!

00:13:57.460 --> 00:13:59.790 align:middle
Ah, he really startled me.

00:14:00.210 --> 00:14:02.250 align:middle
I just blanked out all of a sudden.

00:14:03.790 --> 00:14:05.420 align:middle
Oh, my phone.

00:14:05.420 --> 00:14:07.380 align:middle
Has Ai gone into labor?

00:14:08.130 --> 00:14:09.330 align:middle
Where is my phone anyway?

