01:13:00.670 --> 01:13:06.790 align:middle
Before dawn this morning, a report came in from
her Tokyo condo that "A man is stabbing a woman."

01:13:02.000 --> 01:13:04.830 align:middle
The suspect is a university student

01:13:04.830 --> 01:13:07.670 align:middle
