already dead and my own age,

01:15:34.080 --> 01:15:36.960 align:middle
the police's questioning of me
was limited to simple matters,

01:15:37.380 --> 01:15:40.210 align:middle
but the victim counseling went on for quite some time.

01:15:41.000 --> 01:15:44.250 align:middle
