01:15:49.080 --> 01:15:52.040 align:middle
and you don't need to think of me as your mother...

01:15:52.460 --> 01:15:56.880 align:middle
But, I do think of you two as my own children.

01:15:57.580 --> 01:15:58.580 align:middle
How about it?

01:16:16.380 --> 01:16:17.830 align:middle
Moriizo

01:16:18.420 --> 01:16:22.540 align:middle
