a different job would be quicker and easier,

01:16:31.710 --> 01:16:36.080 align:middle
and the fans are always selfish, and you'll face
a barrage of criticism if you get a boyfriend.

01:16:36.920 --> 01:16:38.880 align:middle
Yeah, even so...

01:16:40.330 --> 01:16:42.250 align:middle
Mama sparkled.

01:16:42.880 --> 01:16:45.250 align:middle
Ruby will probably bounce back...

01:16:45.880 --> 01:16:50.500 align:middle
In my several years living with her I came to understand
she's pure of heart, for better or worse.

01:16:51.710 --> 01:16:52.830 align:middle
But I...

01:16:54.080 --> 01:16:55.960 align:middle
have died once already anyway.

01:16:56.630 --> 01:16:58.920 align:middle
If Ai's not here, then this world...

01:17:03.130 --> 01:17:06.380 align:middle
That stalker and the man who
killed me are one in the same.

01:17:07.170 --> 01:17:09.790 align:middle
How did he pin down the hospital
Ai had been admitted to?

01:17:10.420 --> 01:17:12.750 align:middle
Why'd he come to her new residence
she'd only just moved to?

01:17:13.000 --> 01:17:22.710 align:middle
The darkness of the man

01:17:13.000 --> 01:17:22.710 align:middle
who killed Ai of B Komachi

01:17:13.290 --> 01:17:16.290 align:middle
The culprit was a student
without special skills of any kind.

01:17:16.580 --> 01:17:19.580 align:middle
I simply can't believe he'd be
capable of such detective work.

01:17:20.210 --> 01:17:22.210 align:middle
Someone was feeding him information.

01:17:22.960 --> 01:17:25.880 align:middle
And it must have been someone quite close to Ai.

01:17:26.630 --> 01:17:29.580 align:middle
As far as I know, it was only the president
who knew about her hospital.

01:17:30.000 --> 01:17:33.920 align:middle
But would he do such a thing to the public face of his
agency who he cherished so greatly?

01:17:34.380 --> 01:17:35.330 align:middle
One of her co-workers?

01:17:35.330 --> 01:17:40.960 align:middle
No, the B Komachi girls weren't even that close, and
I never saw anyone who seemed like a good friend of Ai.

01:17:41.460 --> 01:17:44.500 align:middle
It's evident Ai didn't have any relatives who were around,

01:17:44.500 --> 01:17:46.830 align:middle
and it appeared she didn't know
their contact details either...

01:17:47.130 --> 01:17:48.830 align:middle
So that only leaves...

01:17:50.250 --> 01:17:51.880 align:middle
our father.

01:17:52.750 --> 01:17:58.380 align:middle
She stubbornly kept him a secret from the president,
but considering the how narrow Ai's social circle was,

01:17:58.380 --> 01:18:00.830 align:middle
there's a high probability the guy is in the same industry.

01:18:01.330 --> 01:18:04.250 align:middle
Seeing that he and I are related by blood,

01:18:04.880 --> 01:18:07.080 align:middle
I can infer his identify by DNA testing his hair.

01:18:08.040 --> 01:18:12.710 align:middle
The guy who put Ai through all of that
is someone in the entertainment industry.

01:18:14.500 --> 01:18:16.580 align:middle
I can't die yet.

01:18:17.290 --> 01:18:22.080 align:middle
Not until I find him and kill him by my own hand!

01:18:26.080 --> 01:18:26.460 align:middle
Smoking Area

01:18:27.380 --> 01:18:28.460 align:middle
Director.

01:18:27.830 --> 01:18:30.460 align:middle
Smoking Area

01:18:29.000 --> 01:18:30.460 align:middle
Oh, Precocious...

01:18:31.290 --> 01:18:36.460 align:middle
Well, at a time like this, I'm at a loss for what to say.

01:18:36.460 --> 01:18:38.080 align:middle
You don't need to bother with that.

01:18:39.380 --> 01:18:41.830 align:middle
Instead, I'd like to ask a favor of you.

01:18:42.210 --> 01:18:43.040 align:middle
What is it?

01:18:43.750 --> 01:18:45.330 align:middle
Would you consider raising me?

01:18:52.790 --> 01:18:53.750 align:middle
Come on.

01:18:53.750 --> 01:18:55.330 align:middle
You're still not ready, Ruby?

01:18:55.670 --> 01:18:58.630 align:middle
Jeez, just wait a minute, Aqua.

01:18:58.630 --> 01:19:01.630 align:middle
This uniform might be cute, but it's pretty complicated.

01:19:02.500 --> 01:19:04.040 align:middle
But, it sure is cute!

01:19:04.290 --> 01:19:06.670 align:middle
Don't be making us late on the first day, okay?

01:19:08.420 --> 01:19:09.920 align:middle
Isn't your skirt a bit too short?

01:19:09.920 --> 01:19:12.830 align:middle
You know, you've always sounded like an old man.

01:19:14.080 --> 01:19:15.170 align:middle
Oh, that's right!

01:19:16.210 --> 01:19:17.920 align:middle
Mom, we're heading out now.

01:19:24.580 --> 01:19:30.000 align:middle
And thus the prologue concludes,
and the curtain rises on a new tale...

01:19:31.250 --> 01:19:36.920 align:middle
And now, I begin my revenge play.

01:21:11.210 --> 01:21:12.750 align:middle
Is it recording now?

01:21:13.630 --> 01:21:17.000 align:middle
Okay! I thought it would be nice to have this on video.

01:21:27.830 --> 01:21:32.960 align:middle
Once you're grown up, it would be great if we're able
to watch this together while enjoying some alcohol.

01:21:33.540 --> 01:21:37.130 align:middle
Though, I highly doubt I'll still be an idol at that age.

01:21:37.630 --> 01:21:41.540 align:middle
Oh, you two might be idols
yourselves by that point, though!

01:21:41.960 --> 01:21:44.750 align:middle
I mean, you're my kids, so it could totally happen.

01:21:48.210 --> 01:21:52.040 align:middle
In any case, please grow up healthy.

01:21:53.330 --> 01:21:56.460 align:middle
As your mother, that is my sole wish.

